---
layout: layout.njk
title: We’re ready to solve your legal problems
metaTitle: "We’re ready to solve your legal problems. Accepting Clients in Red Deer and Calgary."
description: Accepting Clients in Red Deer and Calgary
button_title: "Contact Us"
button_link: "/contact"
image_url: "/assets/images/home.jpeg"  
main_wrapper_class: "govuk-main-wrapper--no-top-padding"
landing_layout: home

---

{% set serviceItems = collections.services or [] %}
{% if serviceItems | length %}
  <section class="grey-section">
    <div class="govuk-width-container">
      <h2 class="govuk-heading-l">Our Services</h2>
      <p class="govuk-body-lead" style="max-width:60rem">
        Explore the focused legal services AoLaw provides to protect your interests.
      </p>
      <div class="dfe-grid-container">
        {% for service in serviceItems %}
          <div class="dfe-card">
            {% if service.data.icon_url %}
              <div class="dfe-card__media dfe-card__media--icon">
                <img src="{{ service.data.icon_url }}" alt="{{ service.data.title }} icon" class="service-card-icon">
              </div>
            {% elseif service.data.image_url %}
              <div class="dfe-card__media">
                <img src="{{ service.data.image_url }}" alt="{{ service.data.title }}" class="dfe-card__image">
              </div>
            {% endif %}
            <div class="dfe-card-container">
              <h3 class="govuk-heading-m">
                <a class="govuk-link govuk-link--no-visited-state dfe-card-link--header" href="{{ service.url }}">
                  {{ service.data.title }}
                </a>
              </h3>
              {% if service.data.summary %}
                <p class="govuk-body">{{ service.data.summary }}</p>
              {% elseif service.data.description %}
                <p class="govuk-body">{{ service.data.description }}</p>
              {% endif %}
            </div>
          </div>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
{% endif %}
<section class="section" style="padding-bottom:0">
  <div class="govuk-width-container">
     <div class="govuk-grid-row">
       <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
         <h2 class="govuk-heading-l">About Us</h2>
         <p class="govuk-body">At AO Law, we bring years of legal experience, dedication, and professionalism to every case we handle. Founded by Ali Omar, B.A., J.D., our firm is built on a commitment to clear communication, strategic advocacy, and genuine care for our clients.</p>

         <p class="govuk-body">With experience spanning both the United States and Canada, including work with the Atlanta Public Defender’s Office and practice in Alberta’s legal system, we understand the complexities of navigating criminal and civil law.</p>

         <p class="govuk-body">Whether you’re facing a legal dispute, a criminal charge, or simply need guidance through a challenging situation, we approach every case with precision, integrity, and tireless effort. Our goal is simple — to protect your rights and secure the best possible outcome for you. At AO Law, you’re not just another file — you’re our priority.</p>
       </div>
        <div class="govuk-grid-column-one-third">
          <img src="/assets/images/home.jpeg" alt="AO Law office" class="about-image">
        </div>
     </div>
     </div>
    </div>
</section>


  